00:17:29,249 --> 00:17:30,548
Portia,
don't exaggerate.

360
00:17:31,383 --> 00:17:32,717
I'm working on my bike.

361
00:17:32,719 --> 00:17:35,186
You know, they
actually have stores

362
00:17:35,188 --> 00:17:36,754
